 horzpos="0" horzsize="42520" flags="1441792"/></hp:linesegarray></hp:p><hp:p id="0" paraPrIDRef="10" styleIDRef="50" pageBreak="0" columnBreak="0" merged="0"><hp:run charPrIDRef="4"><hp:t>지출 1건당 영수번호를 부여하여 개별 작성해주세요.</hp:t></hp:run><hp:linesegarray><hp:lineseg textpos="0" vertpos="0" vertsize="1100" textheight="1100" baseline="935" spacing="2200" horzpos="0" horzsize="42520" flags="2490368"/></hp:linesegarray></hp:p><hp:p id="0" paraPrIDRef="10" styleIDRef="50" pageBreak="0" columnBreak="0" merged="0"><hp:run charPrIDRef="4"><hp:t>온라인 구매 영수증 등 출력하는 경우는 출력된 영수증에 영수번호, 지출일자, 금액, 내역을 적어서 사용하시면 됩니다. </hp:t></hp:run><hp:linesegarray><hp:lineseg textpos="0" vertpos="0" vertsize="1100" textheight="1100" baseline="935" spacing="2200" horzpos="0" horzsize="42520" flags="2490368"/><hp:lineseg textpos="52" vertpos="0" vertsize="1100" textheight="1100" baseline="935" spacing="2200" horzpos="0" horzsize="42520" flags="1441792"/></hp:linesegarray></hp:p><hp:p id="0" paraPrIDRef="10" styleIDRef="50" pageBreak="0" columnBreak="0" merged="0"><hp:run charPrIDRef="4"><hp:t>영수증은 복사가 가능하도록 겹침 없이 풀로 부착해주세요.</hp:t></hp:run><hp:linesegarray><hp:lineseg textpos="0" vertpos="0" vertsize="1100" textheight="1100" baseline="935" spacing="2200" horzpos="0" horzsize="42520" flags="2490368"/></hp:linesegarray></hp:p><hp:p id="0" paraPrIDRef="10" styleIDRef="50" pageBreak="0" columnBreak="0" merged="0"><hp:run charPrIDRef="4"><hp:t>급여지급증명서, 수령확인증, 이체확인증, 이력서, 계약서, 견적서, 회의록 등의 지출을 증빙하는 관련자료는 영수증과 함께 동일번호로 부여해주세요.</hp:t></hp:run><hp:linesegarray><hp:lineseg textpos="0" vertpos="0" vertsize="1100" textheight="1100" baseline="935" spacing="2200" horzpos="0" horzsize="42520" flags="2490368"/><hp:lineseg textpos="54" vertpos="0" vertsize="1100" textheight="1100" baseline="935" spacing="2200" horzpos="0" horzsize="42520" flags="1441792"/></hp:linesegarray></hp:p></hp:subList><hp:textMargin left="285" right="285" top="285" bottom="285"/></hp:drawText><hc:pt0 x="0" y="0"/><hc:pt1 x="50625" y="0"/><hc:pt2 x